V0510_01_00_00_0.text: If you're ready to Duel, I'm gonna run you over!

V0510_01_00_02_0.text:
You wanna know my Dueling strategy?
It's to win!

V0510_01_00_03_0.text: Quit your yappin' so you can get to losin'!

V0510_01_00_04_0.text:
Bring it!
You'll see how I Duel!

V0510_01_00_05_0.text: If you wanna arrest me, you gotta defeat me first!

V0510_01_00_06_0.text:
Just to double check...
You're really not RinRin?

V0510_01_00_07_0.text: When we were kids, we settled our arguments with a Duel.

V0510_01_00_07_1.text: So if you wanna Duel, I'm game!

V0510_01_00_08_1.text: For the two of us to Duel before a huge crowd!

V0510_03_00_04_0.text: Thanks for reminding me that I gotta focus!

V0510_03_00_05_0.text: I'm not known for giving up!

V0510_05_00_00_0.text:
I can't waste time!
I need a card that'll bring me the win!

V0510_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0510_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0510_11_08_01_0.text:
I build the Overlay Network!
Xyz Summon!

V0510_18_00_01_0.text: You're wide open for a direct attack!

V0510_21_00_01_0.text: I know you got a lot more in ya!

V0510_21_00_03_0.text: That brings my turn to an end!

V0510_21_00_05_0.text: As long as the Duel isn't over, I can still win!

V0510_28_00_00_0.text: That's how ya drive it home!

V0510_28_00_01_0.text: In my city, Dueling's the only way to survive.

V0510_28_00_02_0.text: You need better monsters if you wanna defeat Clear Wing!

V0510_28_00_04_0.text: When I see a chance, I never pass it up.

V0510_28_00_04_1.text: If I did, RinRin would yell at me...

V0510_28_00_05_0.text: In a race, finishing first is everything.

V0510_28_00_06_0.text:
You're good and all...
But you Duel like a textbook.

V0510_28_00_06_1.text:
You gotta loosen up!
Strategize but improvise!

V0510_28_00_07_0.text:
Look, RinRin.
It's Clear Wing Synchro Dragon.
Your favorite.

V0510_28_00_07_1.text: You always said that it'll fly us to victory.

V0510_29_00_01_0.text: RinRin'll be mad if she learns I barely put up a fight.

V0510_29_00_02_0.text:
Aghhh...
I tap! I tap!
You win!

V0510_29_00_03_0.text:
I'll pay you back in double!
Triple!
Million-ple!

V0510_29_00_04_0.text:
You two don't just look alike.
You're tough like her too.

V0510_29_00_05_0.text:
Ouch!
Can't ya ever take it easy?

V0510_33_00_00_0.text: If you find an opportunity, grab it!

V0510_33_00_02_0.text: Giving up is a thing that I just don't do!

V0510_34_00_01_0.text: This isn't a bicycle! It's a Duel Runner!

V0510_34_00_03_0.text: Surrender? I don't even know what that means!

V0510_34_00_04_0.text: This is a great Duel! But let's make it even better!

V0510_34_00_05_0.text: You gotta loosen up your Duel!

V0510_34_00_08_0.text:
I know!
Be quiet for a sec!

V0510_35_00_00_0.text:
The name's Yugo!
Ready to Turbo Duel?

V0510_36_00_02_0.text:
My bad...
But I know you'll turn this Duel around!

V0510_36_00_04_0.text: This should be no problem for you, RinRin!
